git commit â†’ Staging Area â†’ Local Repository

git push â†’ Local Repository â†’ Remote Repository

git pull â†’ Remote Repository â†’ Local Repository + Working Directory

git fetch â†’ Remote Repository â†’ Local Repository (downloads only)

git restore --staged â†’ Staging Area â†’ Working Directory


